  <title>Comments</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>&amp;&amp; characters</keyword>
    <keyword>* character</keyword>
    <keyword>/* characters</keyword>
    <keyword>// characters</keyword>
    <keyword>Adding<keyword>comments</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword>Commands</keyword>
    <keyword>Comments<keyword>adding</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword>NOTE command</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Comments</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">Purpose</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">X# has many comment formats. </para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">Syntax</para>
    <para styleclass="Code with box">/* &#160;this is a multiline <br/> &#160; &#160;comment */<br/>// this is a single line comment<br/>&amp;&amp; this is a single line comment. It may appear after other statements on a line<br/>* this is also a comment. the * must be the first non whitespace character on the line</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">Description</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">X# has many different comment formats</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">Examples</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">These examples show the various comment symbols:</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic; text-decoration:none; color:#339966;">// This is a comment</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic; text-decoration:none; color:#339966;">/* This is a comment */</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic; text-decoration:none; color:#339966;">* This is a comment</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic; text-decoration:none; color:#339966;">&amp;&amp; This is a comment</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
